'''2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会女子公路自行车比赛'''于2008年8月10日举行，共有来自33个国家的66名运动员参加。这是奥运会历史上的第7次女子公路自行车比赛，赛程比以往的任何一次都要长<ref name="Longest">The 2000 race had been the longest, at {{convert|119.7|km|abbr=on}}. {{cite web | url = http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2000/CYC/womens-road-race-individual.html | title = Cycling at the 2000 Sydney Summer Games: Women's Road Race, Individual | publisher = OlyMADMen | work = Sports-Reference | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130925151705/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2000/CYC/womens-road-race-individual.html | archivedate = 2013-09-25 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。比赛在[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会比赛公路自行车赛场|公路自行车赛场]]进行，这一部分赛道共有102.6公里长，加上第二圈约23.8公里的最终部分，本届奥运会女子公路自行车赛的总距离为126.4公里，不到男子自行车赛道距离的一半<ref name="Race">{{cite web |url=http://en.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/headlines/cyclingroad/n214525916.shtml |title=Road Cycling Day 2 Review: Cooke nets soggy gold |publisher=The Beijing Organizing Committee for the Games of the XXIX Olympiad |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328143108/http://en.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/headlines/cyclingroad/n214525916.shtml |date=2008-08-10 |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archivedate=2012-03-28 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Venue">{{cite web |url=http://en.beijing2008.cn/venues/crc/headlines/n214487932.shtml |title=Spectators Guide to Urban Road Cycling Course |publisher=The Beijing Organizing Committee for the Games of the XXIX Olympiad |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606215710/http://en.beijing2008.cn/venues/crc/headlines/n214487932.shtml |archivedate=2014-06-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

比赛期间的降雨给运动员们带来了不便。最终[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会英国代表团|英国队]]选手的[[妮科尔·库克|妮科尔·库克]]赢得了比赛，为该国获得了首枚金牌，这也是英国参加奥运会历史上赢得的第200枚金牌<ref name="Cooke">{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-05-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140506204124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/olympics/cycling/7552294.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/olympics/cycling/7552294.stm | title = Cooke grabs first GB gold medal | work = BBCSport | date = 2008-08-10 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 }}</ref>。[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会瑞典代表团|瑞典]]的[[埃玛·约翰松|埃玛·约翰松]]和[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会意大利代表团|意大利]]的[[塔蒂亚娜·古代尔佐|塔蒂亚娜·古代尔佐]]分别于第二和第三个冲过比赛终点，获得银牌和铜牌。

[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会西班牙代表团|西班牙]]选手玛丽亚·伊莎贝尔·莫里诺（María Isabel Moreno）原定参加这次比赛，但却于7月31日提前离开了北京。[[国际奥林匹克委员会|国际奥林匹克委员会]]于8月11日宣布莫里诺的[[红血球生成素|红血球生成素]]检测结果呈阳性，这也是本届奥运上查出的首例违禁药物事件<ref name="Moreno">{{cite news | url = http://www.cbc.ca/olympics/cycling/story/2008/08/11/olympics-cycling-epotest.html | title = Spanish cyclist tests positive for EPO | work = CBC Sports | date = 2008-08-11 | accessdate = 2008-08-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080906210438/http://www.cbc.ca/olympics/cycling/story/2008/08/11/olympics-cycling-epotest.html | archivedate = 2008-09-06 }}</ref>。这一事件让参赛运动员人数减少到66人，与[[2004年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2004年]]的比赛相比少了一人<ref name="2004Cyclists">{{cite web | url = http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2004/CYC/womens-road-race-individual.html | title = Cycling at the 2004 Athens Summer Games: Women's Road Race, Individual | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131013223117/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2004/CYC/womens-road-race-individual.html | archivedate = 2013-10-13 | publisher = OlyMADMen | work = Sports-Reference | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。
