== 赛前准备 ==
在[[2004年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2004年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]上取得银牌的[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会德国代表团|德国]]选手[[尤迪特·阿恩特|尤迪特·阿恩特]]（{{lang|de|Judith Arndt}}）是本场比赛的大熱門<ref name="cyclingnewspreview" />。阿恩特前不久刚在女子自行车世界杯赛蒙特利尔站夺冠，并且她在奥运会比赛前的几个月里状态一直很好<ref name="Preview">{{cite web |archivedate=2012-09-05 |url=http://en.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/headlines/cyclingroad/n214522963.shtml |title=Road Cycling Day 2 Preview: Women's Road Race |publisher=The Beijing Organizing Committee for the Games of the XXIX Olympiad |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905143831/http://en.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/headlines/cyclingroad/n214522963.shtml |date=2008-08-09 |accessdate=2014-06-29 }}</ref>。其他竞争者包括国际自行车联盟女子公路自行车赛排名最高的[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会荷兰代表团|荷兰]]选手[[玛丽安娜·沃斯|玛丽安娜·沃斯]]<ref name="cyclingnewspreview" />，英国运动员[[妮科尔·库克|妮科尔·库克]]<ref name="cyclingnewspreview" />表示与仅获第5名的2004年相比，这次她对自己的团队更有信心；此外还有意大利车手诺艾米·坎特列（{{lang|en|Noemi Cantele}}）<ref name="cyclingnewspreview">{{cite web | url = http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/road/2008/olympics08/?id=default | title = World's best bound for Beijing | work = Cycling News | author = Greg Johnson | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | archivedate = 2014-01-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140105063645/http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/road/2008/olympics08/?id=default }}</ref>。[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会澳洲代表团|澳大利亚队]]也是一支强队，其中包括卫冕冠军[[萨拉·卡里根|萨拉·卡里根]]<ref name="cyclingnewspreview" />，2008年澳大利亚公路赛冠军[[伊诺尼·伍德|伊诺尼·伍德]]（{{lang|en|Oenone Wood}}）和凯瑟琳·贝茨（{{lang|en|Katherine Bates}}），每人都可以领骑。由于赛道的最后一程包括陡峭的坡道，因此包括库克和沃斯等善于此道的运动员获得看好<ref name="Preview" />。已经49岁的[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会法国代表团|法国]]老将让妮·隆戈（{{lang|en|Jeannie Longo}}）也参加了比赛，她早在[[1984年夏季奥林匹克运动会|1984年]]此项赛事首次成为奥运会比赛项目时就在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]参加了比赛，还曾拿下[[1996年亚特兰大奥运会|1996年亚特兰大奥运会]]的金牌，北京成为她奥运会的第七站<ref name="Preview" /><ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/olympics/cycling/7547703.stm | title = Veteran Longo in no hurry to quit | work = BBC Sport | date = 2008-08-07 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140419030439/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/olympics/cycling/7547703.stm | archivedate = 2014-04-19 }}</ref>。

许多车手估计比赛时北京会非常炎热，因此调整了自己的训练方式来做准备。例如玛丽安娜·沃斯就在[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]进行训练<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130620104756/http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/news.php?id=news%2F2008%2Fmay08%2Fmay09news |url=http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/news.php?id=news/2008/may08/may09news |title=Vos heads South |author=Laura Weislo |date=2008-05-09 |work=CyclingNews |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archivedate=2013-06-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。众车手还预计会遭遇北京严重污染的问题，但这些看起来并没有对[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会男子公路自行车比赛|男子公路自行车赛]]的结果产生影响<ref name="Pollution">{{cite news | publisher = The New York Times Company | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/10/sports/olympics/10cycling.html?ref=sports&_r=0 | title = Humidity Is the Problem in a Race of Attrition | work = The New York Times | author = Greg Bishop | quote = (...) the racers found the real nightmare not in the pollution, but in the humidity and heat. | date = 2008-08-09 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140629032947/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/10/sports/olympics/10cycling.html?ref=sports&_r=0 | archivedate = 2014-06-29 }}</ref>。虽然8月10日北京的污染程度远远超出[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]的安全水平，但比赛期间的降雨减少了雾霾的浓度<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-06-29 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140629033250/http://seattletimes.com/html/nationworld/2008078993_apchinaolympicpollution.html | url = http://seattletimes.com/html/nationworld/2008078993_apchinaolympicpollution.html | title = Beijing air improves with wind and rain | work = The Seattle Times | agency = Associated Press | author = Henry Sanderson | date = 2008-07-29 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 }}</ref><ref name="Transcript">{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-11-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121107221922/http://www.abc.net.au/am/content/2008/s2330631.htm | work = AM | url = http://www.abc.net.au/am/content/2008/s2330631.htm | title = Wet weather disrupts Olympic schedule | publisher = ABC Radio | author = Karen Barlow | date = 2008-08-11 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 }}</ref>。

在前一天举行的男子公路自行车赛上，一些运动员因湿热天气导致发挥受到影响<ref name="Pollution" />。对此部分女性选手选择不穿汗衫。之后的事实证明这一做法得不偿失，因为[[长城|长城]]赛道的气温只有19[[摄氏度|°C]]，远低于前一天的26°C。[[雷暴|雷暴]]带来了持续的强降雨和大风<ref name="Transcript" /><ref name="Live">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618161654/http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/road/2008/olympics08/?id=live%2F2 |deadurl=no |url=http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/road/2008/olympics08/?id=live/2 |title=Women's road race, complete live report |work=Cycling News |author=Susan Westemeyer |date=2008-08-10 |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archivedate=2013-06-18 }}</ref>，这些因素共同影响，导致比赛条件与预计大相径庭<ref name="Cooke" /><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511184851/http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/news.php?id=news%2F2008%2Faug08%2Faug12news2a |url=http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/news.php?id=news/2008/aug08/aug12news2a |title=Vos ready for time trial |date=2008-08-12 |author=Gregor Brown |work=Cycling News |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archivedate=2013-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。包括凯瑟琳·贝茨在内的一些选手在赛前穿上了[[冷冻背心|冷冻背心]]，还在里面放有冰块，结果贝茨没能骑完全程<ref name="Transcript" />。

== 比赛场地 ==
[[Image:Pavillon_des_dix_mille_bonheurs.jpg|thumb]]]]
比赛在[[公路自行车赛场|公路自行车赛场]]举行，这里是北京奥运会的[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会比赛场馆列表|9个临时赛场之一]]，全长102.6公里。与之前的奥运会不同，本次比赛的起点和终点并不一样<ref name="fac">{{cite web | url = http://results.beijing2008.cn/WRM/ENG/BCK/CR/36302.shtml | title = Facility description | accessdate = 2008-09-17 | publisher = The Beijing Organizing Committee for the Games of the XXIX Olympiad | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080917163710/http://results.beijing2008.cn/WRM/ENG/BCK/CR/36302.shtml | archivedate = 2008-09-17 }}</ref>。比赛刚开始时的路径位于北京市中心，地势梯度相对平稳。经过约78.8公里后，众车手将到达长城[[八达岭|八达岭]]赛段，再从八达岭到[[居庸关|居庸关]]骑行两次循环，每次23.8公里<ref name="Race" />。这段路径的地势变得更为陡峭，距起点12.4公里处的高拔高度最高，有338.2米，其中还包括梯度达到10%的陡峭坡道<ref name="Previewmen">{{cite web |url=http://en.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/headlines/cyclingroad/n214516093.shtml |title=Road Cycling Day 1 Preview: Great Wall course serves up cycling vertical challenge |publisher=The Beijing Organizing Committee for the Games of the XXIX Olympiad |date=2008-08-08 |accessdate=2014-06-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905143437/http://en.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/headlines/cyclingroad/n214516093.shtml |archivedate=2012-09-05 }}</ref>。这一点后车手们会经过一段相对平整的路程，再进入朝向居庸关的高速公路。最后350米是一段中等程度的斜坡，目的是让多位骑手可以聚集在一起，给比赛带来扣人心弦的的最后冲刺<ref name="Previewmen" />。这场女子自行车公路赛全程长126.4公里，还不到男子比赛路程的一半<ref name="Race" /><ref name="Venue" />。

比赛起点位于[[永定门|永定门]]，这里属北京北部的[[崇文区|崇文区]]，是该市[[城墙|老城墙]]的遗留部分。赛程从城市进入相对偏远的乡村，共计经过了8个地区：崇文区、[[宣武区|宣武区]]、[[东城区_(北京市)|东城区]]、[[西城区|西城区]]、[[朝阳区_(北京市)|朝阳区]]、[[海淀区|海淀区]]、[[昌平区|昌平区]]和[[延庆县|延庆县]]，一路上可以看到诸如[[天坛|天坛]]、[[人民大会堂|人民大会堂]]、[[天安门广场|天安门广场]]、[[雍和宫|雍和宫]]和[[长城|长城]]等地标式的建筑物<ref name="Venue" />。还通过了2008年奥运会的多个特色建筑，如[[国家体育场_(北京)|国家体育场]]和[[国家游泳中心|国家游泳中心]]（通称“鸟巢”和“水立方”）<ref name="Guardian" />。赛道终点位于昌平区居庸关，《[[卫报|卫报]]》称赞这段路程的风景是一场“视觉盛宴”<ref name="Guardian">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130930151338/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2008/aug/09/olympicscycling.olympics2008 | url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2008/aug/09/olympicscycling.olympics2008 | title = Olympics: Sanchez clinches road race gold for Spain | work = The Guardian | author = William Fotherington | date = 2008-08-09 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | location = London | archivedate = 2013-09-30 }}</ref>。

考虑到安全因素，奥运会的组织者禁止观众站在赛道边观看比赛。这一决定引起了争议：很多自行车界的名人，如[[国际自行车联合会|国际自联]]主席[[帕特·麦魁德|帕特·麦魁德]]（{{lang|en|Pat McQuaid}}）、澳大利亚自行车运动员[[斯图尔特·奥格雷迪|斯图尔特·奥格雷迪]]和[[卡德尔·埃文斯|卡德尔·埃文斯]]都反对这一举措。麦魁德和奥格雷迪都认为赛道边上没有观众会影响比赛的气氛，而且批评赛事的组织者没有考虑到希望近距离观看比赛的观众<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2008-12-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081222234118/http://www.aol.co.nz/news/story/UCI-head-regrets-lack-of-spectators-at-road-race/847311/index.html | deadurl = yes | title = UCI head regrets lack of spectators at road race | publisher = AOL | url = http://www.aol.co.nz/news/story/UCI-head-regrets-lack-of-spectators-at-road-race/847311/index.html | date = 2008-08-13 | accessdate = 2008-12-22 }}</ref>。[[澳大利亚自行车协会|澳大利亚自行车协会]]对此要求在接下来的[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会男子公路自行车个人计时赛|个人计时赛]]中放宽这方面限制<ref name="headache">{{cite web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120918014114/http://news.ninemsn.com.au/olympics/article.aspx?id=611959 | archivedate = 2012-09-18 | url = http://news.ninemsn.com.au/olympics/article.aspx?id=611959 | title = Cycling race 'was silent murder' | agency = Associated Press | author = Mat Mackay | date = 2008-08-10 | accessdate = 2012-09-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = 'Ghost course' haunts cyclists Stuart O'Grady and Cadel Evans | author = Ben English | work = The Australian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140629062649/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/ghost-course-haunts-cyclists/story-e6frg6n6-1111117153315?nk=83a71ad3929aee65ea6b342d872dcdf8 | archivedate = 2014-06-29 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/ghost-course-haunts-cyclists/story-e6frg6n6-1111117153315?nk=83a71ad3929aee65ea6b342d872dcdf8 | date = 2008-08-10 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 }}</ref>，但最终组织者并没有这么做<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/cycle-families-kept-away-again/story-e6frg6n6-1111117176242 | title = China ignores pleas for better access to the cycling route | author = Leo Schlink | work = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2008-08-13 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | via = The Australian}}</ref>。

== 比赛 ==
[[Image:Arndt0106_543.jpg|thumb]]
比赛于[[中国时区|北京时间]]下午14点开始（[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]早上6点），计划在17点30分结束<ref name="TeamGB">{{cite web | url = http://www.olympics.org.uk/beijing2008/ScheduleDetailed.aspx?SP=CYR#a10-08-2008 | title = Team GB > Beijing 2008 > Schedule Details | accessdate = 2008-05-29 | publisher = Team GB – British Olympics Association | archivedate = 2008-05-29 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080529081732/http://www.olympics.org.uk/beijing2008/ScheduleDetailed.aspx?SP=CYR#a10-08-2008 }}</ref>。天气异常凉爽，比赛开始时是阴天，路面也很干爽。比赛中途开始下雨并持续到结束，雨量虽然基本稳定，但还是加大了选手的竞赛难度<ref name="Race" />。

比赛过程中出现了一些变故，导致骑手损失了宝贵的时间。[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会韩国代表团|韩国]]车手谷孙根的[[自行车|自行车]]失控，致使其他多名运运员一起摔倒，她自己则摔进了高速公路一侧的混凝土沟<ref name="Live" />。[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会俄罗斯代表团|俄罗斯]]的纳塔利娅·博亚尔斯卡娅（{{lang|en|Natalia Boyarskaya}}）一度在八达岭赛段顶部积累了59秒的领先优势<ref name="Race" />，但却由于路口标识欠佳而只好停下来查看自己应该选择哪条岔路<ref name="Live"/><ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/olympics/live_action/7551996.stm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080906224347/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/olympics/live_action/7551996.stm | title = Olympics day two as it happened | work = BBC Sport | date = 2008-08-10 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | archivedate = 2008-09-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会美国代表团|美国]]选手[[克莉丝汀·托尔布恩|克莉丝汀·托尔布恩]]（{{lang|en|Christine Thorburn}}）在追逐中接替了博亚尔斯卡娅的领先地位，到比赛还剩最后一圈、23.8公里路程时领先幅度还剩34秒。[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会英国代表团|英国队]]的[[埃玛·普利|埃玛·普利]]和[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会意大利代表团|意大利队]]的[[塔蒂亚娜·古代尔佐|塔蒂亚娜·古代尔佐]]在距终点还剩22公里处追上了博亚尔斯卡娅，德国队也以稳健的步伐在不久后追上三人<ref name="Race" />。古代尔佐在最后13公里处发起冲刺，[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会奥地利代表团|奥地利]]的克里斯蒂安·索德（{{lang|en|Christiane Soeder}}）、[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会瑞典代表团|瑞典]]的[[埃玛·约翰松|埃玛·约翰松]]、英国的妮科尔·库克和[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会丹麦代表团|丹麦]]的[[琳达·维鲁姆森|琳达·维鲁姆森]]（{{lang|en|Linda Villumsen}}）随后加入。这几名运动员与[[大部队|大部队]]保持有16秒的领先优势。赛前普遍看好的玛丽安娜·沃斯和朱迪斯·阿恩特未能加入领先团队，沃斯犹豫了一下之后再与阿恩特一起进入大部队的领先位置<ref name="Race" />。库克在最后一个转变处还只排在第5位，但却在距终点只剩200米处成功取得领先，以明显优势夺得金牌。约翰松和古代尔佐分获银牌和铜牌，沃斯同其他多名选手一起冲过终点线，与冠军相差了21秒<ref name="Race" />。

据事后透露，库克使用的是轻巧型轮胎，不适合在雨天比赛，所以有意在前面的比赛过程中保持实力<ref name="Perfection">{{cite news | archivedate = 2012-11-10 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121110085014/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/2535990/Timing-to-perfection-as-Nicole-Cooke-wins-gold-in-womens-cycling-road-race-at-Games.html | author = Brendan Gallagher | work = The Telegraph | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/2535990/Timing-to-perfection-as-Nicole-Cooke-wins-gold-in-womens-cycling-road-race-at-Games.html | title = Timing to perfection as Nicole Cooke wins gold in women's cycling road race at Games | date = 2008-08-10 | location = London }}</ref>。她的公路车队经理朱利安·温（{{lang|en|Julian Winn}}）表示：我们担心有人会在前面摔倒，所以让她保持在左侧。我们知道她后面就会追上去的<ref name="Homework">{{cite news | url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2008/aug/11/olympicscycling.olympics20082 | title = Olympics: Cooke does her homework and gives Britain first gold of Games | author = William Fotheringham | work = The Guardian | date = 2008-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140412203551/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2008/aug/11/olympicscycling.olympics20082 | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | location = London | archivedate = 2014-04-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。库克的胜利是精心策划的成果<ref name="Perfection" />，她的团队在赛前就已骑完全程，并制定了取胜计划<ref name="Homework" />。

== 兴奋剂事件 ==
比赛前一天，[[国际奥林匹克委员会|国际奥林匹克委员会]]的一位发言人宣布，西班牙骑手玛丽亚·伊莎贝尔·莫里诺没有通过药检，这也成为本届奥运会上查出的首例违禁药物检测阳性事件<ref name="Guardian2">{{cite news | archivedate = 2013-12-28 | url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2008/aug/11/olympicscycling.olympics20083?gusrc=rss&feed=sport | title = Spanish cyclist Moreno tests positive for EPO | work = The Guardian | author = Staff and agencies | date = 2008-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131228170148/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2008/aug/11/olympicscycling.olympics20083?gusrc=rss&feed=sport | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | location = London | deadurl = no }}</ref>。莫里诺于7月31日飞抵北京并提供了[[尿液分析|尿样]]，但当天就出现[[恐慌发作|恐慌发作]]而飞回[[马德里|马德里]]，之后也没有再回来参赛。她的尿样经检验发现[[红血球生成素|红血球生成素]]呈阳性。国际奥委会剥夺了莫里诺的参赛资格，之后再向国际自行车联盟转达了这一决定和确认的阳性结果。莫里诺的网站发表声明，表示自己还不准备对离开奥运村的原因作出解释<ref name="Guardian2" />。

== 比赛结果 ==
共计66名车手获得了参赛资格，预计其中很多并不会骑完全程，只是为了帮助队友，在前方领骑<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.csc.com/cycling/news/8782-olympics_cancellara_mines_bronze_in_beijing | title = Olympics: Cancellara Mines Bronze in Beijing | publisher = Computer Sciences Corporation (CSC) | quote = (...) riders raced for the respective national squads in international competition. | date = 2008-08-09 | accessdate = 2008-12-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081203144205/http://www.csc.com/cycling/news/8782-olympics_cancellara_mines_bronze_in_beijing | archivedate = 2008-12-03 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，让他们可以在良好的位置上发挥更出色的爬坡能力<ref>{{cite web | url = http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/results/2001/diary01/b_jones_thuringen.shtml | title = Ups and downs | author = Brice Jones | work = Cycling News | accessdate = 2014-06-29 | archivedate = 2013-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002163640/http://autobus.cyclingnews.com/results/2001/diary01/b_jones_thuringen.shtml }}</ref>。此外，任何在八达岭赛段落后领先骑手达一整圈的运动员都将被强制退出<ref>{{cite web | url = http://results.beijing2008.cn/WRM/ENG/BCK/CR/36318.shtml | title = Competition format and rules | publisher = The Beijing Organizing Committee for the Games of the XXIX Olympiad | date = 2008-08-08 | accessdate = 2008-12-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081224002830/http://results.beijing2008.cn/WRM/ENG/BCK/CR/36318.shtml | archivedate = 2008-12-24 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，不过实际比赛中并没有出现这样的情况。以下表格列出了本次比赛的结果，“同上”表示该选手通过终点的时间与上一名次选手相同。

